node.text:
Alive We Ride, the anthem of a generation that even today, still rings True To This.  The first of its kind, this film galvanized Volcom as Americas First Boarding Company.  There is just one problem, in 1993 licensing music for a VHS release was a lot different than the digital abyss of now.  But we have you covered with a Spotify playlist of the original soundtrack! 
http://vol.cm/awrplaylist
Just like driving a stick shift, grab your boombox and watch this in manual!  Or pop on your favorite playlist… Or create a new one all together and put your personal stamp on it!
